Fri Aug 20 11:33:28 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* layout.tcl:
	  Added a command to throw all nodes connected to a
	  network into a group. Nodes with more than one link
	  (gateways) are excluded.

	* manager.tcl:
	  A new menu entry allows the user to interactively specify
	  which interpreter should be started.

Thu Aug 19 11:29:54 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* monitor.tcl:
	  The RPC based monitoring tools check the reach-ability
	  of the nodes using icmp. This reduces the RPC timeout
	  for inactive hosts.

	* utils.tcl:
	  select member allows you to select all members of an
	  expanded group.

Wed Jul 28 16:30:58 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* layout.tcl:
	  Unknown icon mappings are now shown at the end of
	  the process.

	* discover.tcl:
	  Discovering route is now done in the same way a whole
	  network gets discovered. This allows us to mix both
	  operations.

Tue Jul 27 11:50:34 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* discover.tcl:
	  Added the ability to add new discovered nodes to an
	  existing map. An existing node or a network is recognized 
	  based on its address attribute.

	* monitor.tcl:
	  The check reach-ability and round trip time commands now
	  use the ability to send all icmp requests in parallel.

Tue Jul 26 18:36:50 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* discover.tcl:
	  Discover Route command added that traces a route to
	  the current selection and adds all intermediate nodes
	  to the current map.

Tue Jul 22 17:34:37 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* trouble.tcl:
	  dns info command added that displays dns information.

Thu Jul 21 18:51:15 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* the dns command written by Erik Schoenfelder is now
	  used to get hinfo records.

Thu Jul 19 19:45:15 1993  Juergen Schoenwaelder  (schoenw@bayes)

	* scotty-0.5 released (first public release)

